04:40.040 --> 04:42.120
<font color="#00ffff">We must talk about my title.</font>

04:42.720 --> 04:44.400
We have talked about it, Mama.

04:45.360 --> 04:48.280
<font color="#00ffff">It seems your Lord Melbourne</font>
<font color="#00ffff">turned you against me.</font>

04:48.320 --> 04:50.880
I make my own decisions.

04:50.920 --> 04:55.120
And I see no reason to make you
Queen Mother, however much Sir John
might like it.

04:55.160 --> 04:57.720
<font color="#00ffff">It is a shame you don't have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a bigger head, Drina.</font>

04:58.360 --> 05:00.800
<font color="#00ffff">It is too small for the crown, I</font>
<font color="#00ffff">think.</font>

05:09.920 --> 05:11.040
(Clattering)

05:11.080 --> 05:15.000
There are workmen with dirty boots
in my kitchen, Mr Penge.

05:15.400 --> 05:17.760
I'm trying to make a cake
for the Queen's birthday,

05:17.800 --> 05:20.120
a cake that will dazzle the court
with its artistry.

05:20.160 --> 05:22.280
But how can I reach
the very pinnacle of my craft

05:22.320 --> 05:25.200
when I'm surrounded by noise and
dust and whistling?

05:25.240 --> 05:28.800
<font color="#ffff00">Don't blame me, Mr Francatelli,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">blame the Baroness.</font>

05:28.840 --> 05:31.320
<font color="#ffff00">She's the one that ordered the gas</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to be put in.</font>

05:31.360 --> 05:34.800
<font color="#ffff00">Though why they had to start down</font>
<font color="#ffff00">here I will never know.</font>

05:34.840 --> 05:38.080
You must tell the Baroness that I
cannot work under these conditions.

05:38.120 --> 05:41.600
<font color="#ffff00">Try telling the Baroness anything.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">She sets great store by the Queen's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">birthday.</font>

05:41.640 --> 05:45.880
<font color="#00ff00">If you told her the cake wouldn't be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">ready, she would want Mr Francatelli</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to work in peace.</font>

05:45.920 --> 05:47.960
Oh, thank you, Miss...?
<font color="#00ff00">Skerrett, sir.</font>

05:48.000 --> 05:50.400
<font color="#00ffff">Hmph! What are you doing?</font>

05:50.800 --> 05:53.160
<font color="#00ffff">Dressers don't curtsey to cooks.</font>

05:53.200 --> 05:55.200
Oh, but I am not a cook, I am a
chef.

05:56.240 --> 05:59.360
<font color="#00ffff">Oh! And let there be light!</font>

06:00.880 --> 06:02.560
<font color="#00ffff">(Screaming)</font>

06:03.840 --> 06:07.040
<font color="#ffff00">That's what happens</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when you interfere with nature.</font>

06:07.080 --> 06:09.200
<font color="#00ff00">I'll get them.</font>

06:09.240 --> 06:11.240
Will you be very long, Mr Hayter?

06:11.280 --> 06:13.320
The crown is so heavy and far too
big for me.

06:13.360 --> 06:16.680
I thought it might slip down over my
nose in the Abbey.

06:16.720 --> 06:18.720
<font color="#00ffff">Really, Ma'am? You looked so serene.</font>

06:18.760 --> 06:22.880
My heart was beating so fast I
thought the Archbishop would see it
through my shift.

06:22.920 --> 06:25.520
Lord M said he had never seen
someone tremble so.

06:25.560 --> 06:27.560
<font color="#00ffff">He told me he thought you did it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">beautifully.</font>

06:30.200 --> 06:33.240
VICTORIA: I am concerned about him.
He does not seem himself.

06:33.280 --> 06:37.120
<font color="#00ffff">My husband said they are worried</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about the Jamaica Bill. There is a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">lot of opposition.</font>

06:37.160 --> 06:41.440
<font color="#ffff00">Your Uncle Cumberland would like</font>
<font color="#ffff00">nothing better than to bring down</font>
<font color="#ffff00">poor William.</font>

06:41.480 --> 06:44.720
<font color="#ffff00">The funny thing is, a few weeks ago</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he would have been delighted.</font>

06:44.760 --> 06:48.720
<font color="#00ffff">He was always complaining about</font>
<font color="#00ffff">how tiresome it was being Prime</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Minister.</font>

06:48.760 --> 06:50.840
<font color="#ffff00">But not any more.</font>

06:50.880 --> 06:52.680
<font color="#00ff00">(Clears throat)</font>

06:54.040 --> 06:55.240
Order!

06:55.280 --> 07:00.320
My Lords, I call for a vote
on the Jamaica Bill.

07:00.360 --> 07:05.480
The ayes to the right,
the no's to the left, gentlemen.

07:15.400 --> 07:18.280
<font color="#ffff00">Look, Mr Penge, reckon I could catch</font>
<font color="#ffff00">all of them by midnight.</font>

07:18.320 --> 07:22.680
You just leave those rats alone,
boy. I've got plans for them, big
plans.

07:24.000 --> 07:28.480
It can only be described as an
infestation.

07:28.520 --> 07:34.000
That's the trouble with gas, it
shines light on things you would
rather not see.

07:34.040 --> 07:39.440
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen must not know.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">She has a great fear of these</font>
<font color="#00ffff">animals.</font>

07:39.480 --> 07:43.880
So you are authorising me to hire a
rat catcher?

07:43.920 --> 07:48.480
With all the extra expense that
entails?

07:48.520 --> 07:50.480
<font color="#00ffff">You must find an expert.</font>

07:51.320 --> 07:53.640
Certainly, Baroness.

08:16.240 --> 08:20.240
<font color="#00ffff">I think you will be impressed,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Majesty, when the gas lighting is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">finally installed.</font>

08:20.280 --> 08:22.680
I hope Lord M won't be much longer.

08:22.720 --> 08:27.040
I so want to show him the painting I
did of Dash. He said it couldn't be
done.

08:27.080 --> 08:29.960
<font color="#00ffff">Shall I ring for some Negus,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Majesty?</font>

08:30.000 --> 08:32.720
<font color="#00ffff">You know how soothing you find it at</font>
<font color="#00ffff">night.</font>

08:32.760 --> 08:34.320
He should be here by now.

08:34.360 --> 08:36.640
<font color="#ffff00">Sometimes the voting can take ages,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>

08:36.679 --> 08:39.000
(Neighing of horse
and distant carriage wheels)

08:39.039 --> 08:40.799
There's his carriage.

08:51.160 --> 08:52.880
Lord M!

08:54.720 --> 08:57.440
The others had given you up
but I knew you would come.

08:57.480 --> 09:02.360
I must show you a painting I did of
Dash. I got him to sit still for just
long enough.

09:02.400 --> 09:03.880
<font color="#ffff00">That's a feat in itself.</font>

09:05.000 --> 09:08.000
<font color="#ffff00">I...I must...tell you, Ma'am,</font>

09:09.000 --> 09:13.600
<font color="#ffff00">the Jamaica Bill passed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">by only five votes this evening.</font>

09:15.200 --> 09:18.160
<font color="#ffff00">And that means I can no longer lead</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Whigs in government.</font>

09:20.040 --> 09:22.280
But if the bill passed, why should
you resign?

09:22.320 --> 09:24.040
<font color="#ffff00">The Tories are like hyenas, Ma'am.</font>

09:24.080 --> 09:27.000
<font color="#ffff00">Once they scent a man is down,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">they circle looking for weaknesses.</font>

09:27.040 --> 09:30.520
<font color="#ffff00">The next vote we would certainly</font>
<font color="#ffff00">lose. I'd rather leave now.</font>

09:33.640 --> 09:35.440
This cannot be.

09:37.040 --> 09:38.360
How can I...?

09:38.960 --> 09:40.680
How will I...?

09:49.920 --> 09:52.720
Do you really mean to forsake me?

09:56.240 --> 09:58.080
<font color="#ffff00">I have no choice, Ma'am.</font>

10:14.520 --> 10:16.920
(Thunder rumbles)

10:16.960 --> 10:19.920
(Grunts and sobs)

10:32.080 --> 10:33.880
<font color="#00ff00">My poor Victoria.</font>

10:34.720 --> 10:36.680
<font color="#00ff00">Such a big change.</font>

10:39.960 --> 10:41.720
How will I manage?

10:41.760 --> 10:43.880
<font color="#00ff00">I know how you're feeling.</font>

10:43.920 --> 10:47.080
<font color="#00ff00">To be a woman without a man to lean</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on is so hard.</font>

10:47.120 --> 10:49.680
He is the only one who understands.

10:49.720 --> 10:52.000
<font color="#00ff00">No. Not the only one.</font>

11:01.600 --> 11:03.640
(Sobs) Oh, Mama.

11:23.080 --> 11:24.280
(Knock at door)

11:24.320 --> 11:26.200
<font color="#00ffff">LEHZEN: Please open the door,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Majesty.</font>

11:26.760 --> 11:29.800
<font color="#00ffff">If you don't get up now,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">there won't be time to get ready.</font>

11:29.840 --> 11:31.360
(Dog yaps)

11:31.400 --> 11:33.960
(Continues yapping)

11:34.000 --> 11:36.240
<font color="#ffff00">You don't suppose</font>
<font color="#ffff00">she's done something stupid?</font>

11:36.280 --> 11:38.440
<font color="#00ffff">Never! It is just some nerves.</font>

11:38.480 --> 11:41.880
<font color="#00ff00">Excuse me, Your Grace, but have</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you informed Lord Melbourne?</font>

11:41.920 --> 11:44.160
<font color="#00ff00">He is so good at putting the Queen</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in a good humour.</font>

11:44.200 --> 11:46.760
<font color="#00ff00">Brodie could take a message to Dover</font>
<font color="#00ff00">House in no time.</font>

11:49.440 --> 11:51.520
MELBOURNE: "I strongly suggest,
Ma'am,

11:51.560 --> 11:54.320
that you ask the Duke of Wellington
to form a government.

11:56.560 --> 11:58.960
He is, of course, a Tory...

12:00.520 --> 12:02.040
..but better the devil you know."

12:19.720 --> 12:21.600
<font color="#00ffff">The Duke of Wellington.</font>

12:29.160 --> 12:32.360
I understand that I am obliged
to ask you to form a government.

12:32.400 --> 12:35.280
Lord Melbourne says he no longer
has the confidence of the House

12:35.320 --> 12:37.000
and that your party must take
charge.

12:37.040 --> 12:38.600
<font color="#00ff00">You do me a great honour, Ma'am.</font>

12:38.640 --> 12:42.040
<font color="#00ff00">But I regret that I am too old</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to be Prime Minister again.</font>

12:42.080 --> 12:44.480
<font color="#00ff00">It is time to make way for a younger</font>
<font color="#00ff00">man.</font>

12:44.520 --> 12:47.520
<font color="#00ff00">You should send for Robert Peel.</font>

12:47.560 --> 12:52.280
But I do not know Sir Robert,
and I have admired you all my life.

12:52.320 --> 12:53.480
<font color="#00ff00">You flatter me, Ma'am,</font>

12:53.520 --> 12:58.280
<font color="#00ff00">but I'm afraid that this is a</font>
<font color="#00ff00">battle... you cannot win.</font>

13:02.640 --> 13:06.520
<font color="#ffff00">Look at the mud on these. Very</font>
<font color="#ffff00">unlike Ma'am to get her things so</font>
<font color="#ffff00">dirty.</font>

13:06.560 --> 13:09.160
<font color="#00ffff">I think Her Majesty is distracted.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

13:09.200 --> 13:13.960
<font color="#ffff00">We wouldn't put in our curl papers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">last night. The pillow was wet</font>
<font color="#ffff00">through this morning.</font>

13:14.000 --> 13:18.440
<font color="#00ffff">I feel sorry for the Queen. She is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so attached to Lord Melbourne.</font>

13:19.680 --> 13:23.680
<font color="#ffff00">Whatever she thinks of Lord</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Melbourne does not concern you.</font>

13:23.720 --> 13:26.200
<font color="#ffff00">We just...take care of the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">clothes...</font>

13:27.760 --> 13:30.640
<font color="#ffff00">..and make sure...she looks like a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Queen.</font>

13:31.520 --> 13:33.120
<font color="#ffff00">Now then...</font>

13:35.480 --> 13:37.440
<font color="#ffff00">..how do you turn this thing on?</font>

13:41.760 --> 13:44.040
<font color="#ffff00">Aagh!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, Mrs Jenkins!</font>

13:44.080 --> 13:47.040
<font color="#00ffff">I'll shall fetch some butter from</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the kitchen.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Oh!</font>

13:47.960 --> 13:49.400
<font color="#00ffff">May I have some butter?</font>

13:49.440 --> 13:52.040
<font color="#00ffff">It's for Mrs Jenkins.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">She burnt her hand lighting the gas.</font>

13:52.080 --> 13:55.640
You can have butter if you like,
but I can give you something better.

13:55.680 --> 13:57.520
<font color="#00ffff">You can?</font>

14:02.080 --> 14:04.560
Close your eyes.
<font color="#00ffff">Not likely.</font>

14:04.600 --> 14:06.920
<font color="#00ffff">You might do something complicated.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, please.</font>

14:06.960 --> 14:08.920
Or you'll spoil my surprise.

14:18.680 --> 14:20.560
<font color="#00ffff">Oh-ah-ha-ha!</font>

14:21.960 --> 14:23.360
<font color="#00ffff">An ice house!</font>

14:23.400 --> 14:25.600
<font color="#00ffff">I had heard about them, but...</font>

14:25.640 --> 14:29.280
There's something about your very
charming face that's familiar.

14:29.320 --> 14:31.040
Could we have met before?

14:31.080 --> 14:33.120
<font color="#00ffff">I don't think so.</font>

14:33.160 --> 14:35.280
<font color="#00ffff">I had better get back to Mrs</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Jenkins.</font>

14:49.480 --> 14:51.240
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty.</font>

14:51.600 --> 14:54.960
<font color="#00ff00">One moment...Ma'am.</font>

14:56.600 --> 15:00.040
<font color="#00ff00">I imagine the change of government</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is unsettling.</font>

15:00.720 --> 15:03.080
<font color="#00ff00">I know how much you value</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Lord Melbourne's counsel.</font>

15:03.120 --> 15:06.040
<font color="#00ff00">But you have...other friends, Ma'am.</font>

15:06.080 --> 15:09.160
<font color="#00ff00">In contrast to your estimable Uncle</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Cumberland,</font>

15:09.200 --> 15:12.880
<font color="#00ff00">I should like to assure you of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">my...loyalty.</font>

15:13.880 --> 15:17.520
<font color="#00ff00">The Duchess and I are ready to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">shoulder the burden of government.</font>

15:17.560 --> 15:19.760
I shall not need your assistance.

15:19.800 --> 15:22.560
<font color="#00ff00">Hmm. With respect, Ma'am...</font>

15:24.400 --> 15:26.840
<font color="#00ff00">..that may not be your decision.</font>

15:29.880 --> 15:32.400
<font color="#ffff00">It's all on account of the gas</font>
<font color="#ffff00">pipes.</font>

15:32.440 --> 15:34.960
<font color="#ffff00">They must be dealt with discreetly.</font>

15:36.280 --> 15:38.680
<font color="#ffff00">Her Majesty don't like rodents.</font>

15:38.720 --> 15:42.800
Big job, mind, a place like this.
I'll have to charge royal prices.

15:42.840 --> 15:45.080
<font color="#ffff00">I am sure we can come to an</font>
<font color="#ffff00">arrangement as to fees</font>

15:45.120 --> 15:49.600
<font color="#ffff00">but you should be aware that,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as the steward, I take an emolument.</font>

15:51.280 --> 15:54.040
Well, it's only to be expected, Mr
Penge.

15:54.080 --> 15:58.320
<font color="#ffff00">And if it should be found rats</font>
<font color="#ffff00">reached as far as the state rooms,</font>

15:58.360 --> 16:00.960
<font color="#ffff00">of course you would need</font>
<font color="#ffff00">many more assistants.</font>

16:02.840 --> 16:05.840
<font color="#00ffff">Well, you are a master of the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">situation, Mr Penge.</font>

16:08.600 --> 16:11.680
I sent for Lord M hours ago.
Why hasn't he come?

16:11.720 --> 16:16.160
<font color="#ffff00">I imagine, Ma'am, that he is waiting</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for you to talk to Sir Robert Peel.</font>

16:17.120 --> 16:19.080
Why would I do that?

16:20.040 --> 16:22.600
<font color="#ffff00">Because, Ma'am, the country needs a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">government,</font>

16:22.640 --> 16:27.040
<font color="#ffff00">and at this moment it seems that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">only Sir Robert has the confidence</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of the House.</font>

16:30.680 --> 16:33.160
<font color="#00ffff">I hear that Wellington has refused</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you.</font>

16:33.200 --> 16:35.960
<font color="#00ffff">But don't worry, Sir John and I will</font>
<font color="#00ffff">help you. We have a plan.</font>

16:39.120 --> 16:41.400
As it happens, I also have a plan.

16:41.440 --> 16:43.240
Lehzen, can you call my carriage?

16:43.280 --> 16:45.720
I'm going to go to Dover House to
see Lord M.

16:45.760 --> 16:47.480
<font color="#00ffff">Have you lost your mind, Drina?</font>

16:47.520 --> 16:50.280
<font color="#00ffff">Queens do not chase after their</font>
<font color="#00ffff">prime ministers.</font>

16:51.680 --> 16:54.160
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps, Ma'am, you should take my</font>
<font color="#ffff00">carriage.</font>

16:54.200 --> 16:57.720
<font color="#ffff00">It would be less...public.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Do you really want to make another</font>
<font color="#00ffff">mistake?</font>

16:57.760 --> 17:02.240
Yes. Thank you, Emma, I will take
your carriage. Lehzen, you can be my
chaperone.

17:26.599 --> 17:29.760
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not to be disturbed!</font>

17:29.800 --> 17:31.320
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty.</font>

17:32.960 --> 17:34.840
That will be all, Lehzen.

17:37.480 --> 17:39.040
(Door closes)

17:40.080 --> 17:42.680
As you would not visit me, I decided
to visit you!

17:43.960 --> 17:47.240
<font color="#ffff00">Forgive my disarray.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I...I was not expecting visitors.</font>

17:48.920 --> 17:51.280
Evidently!
<font color="#ffff00">(Chuckles)</font>

17:51.320 --> 17:52.760
(Chuckles)

17:53.880 --> 17:56.720
<font color="#ffff00">Please. At least...</font>

17:56.760 --> 17:58.840
<font color="#ffff00">Come...</font>

17:58.880 --> 18:00.400
<font color="#ffff00">Come sit.</font>

18:01.120 --> 18:04.600
<font color="#ffff00">You can tell me what has brought you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from the Palace.</font>

18:13.960 --> 18:15.600
I saw the Duke of Wellington.

18:15.640 --> 18:18.840
He has refused to form a ministry
and says I must send for Sir Robert
Peel.

18:18.880 --> 18:20.880
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, I thought he might.</font>

18:20.920 --> 18:25.560
I don't want Sir Robert Peel. Lord
M, how can you leave me to face this,
alone?

18:25.600 --> 18:27.840
<font color="#ffff00">Do you imagine that I want to leave</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you, Ma'am?</font>

18:28.720 --> 18:32.240
<font color="#ffff00">There is something more important</font>
<font color="#ffff00">here than my feelings, or even</font>
<font color="#ffff00">yours.</font>

18:32.280 --> 18:34.600
<font color="#ffff00">You are the Queen of the greatest</font>
<font color="#ffff00">nation on earth,</font>

18:34.640 --> 18:37.920
<font color="#ffff00">one that elects its government</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and abides by the rule of law.</font>

18:37.960 --> 18:40.080
<font color="#ffff00">Now I don't believe in much, as you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">know,</font>

18:40.120 --> 18:43.720
<font color="#ffff00">but I do believe in the British</font>
<font color="#ffff00">constitution in all its tattered</font>
<font color="#ffff00">glory,</font>

18:43.760 --> 18:49.280
<font color="#ffff00">and nothing, not even my devotion to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you, will stop me from upholding it.</font>

18:52.640 --> 18:54.520
I see.

18:54.560 --> 18:56.320
<font color="#ffff00">Peel's not such a bad fellow really.</font>

18:56.360 --> 19:00.720
<font color="#ffff00">Just remember, if he suggests</font>
<font color="#ffff00">anything that you don't like the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">sound of,</font>

19:00.760 --> 19:02.760
<font color="#ffff00">just ask him for a little time to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">consider.</font>

19:02.800 --> 19:04.320
<font color="#ffff00">When in doubt, always delay.</font>

19:04.360 --> 19:07.280
And you will come for dinner tonight
so I can tell you all about it?

19:07.320 --> 19:10.240
<font color="#ffff00">No! Not tonight. Not until this</font>
<font color="#ffff00">matter is settled.</font>

19:10.280 --> 19:13.120
<font color="#ffff00">And even then, I cannot be at the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Palace as much as I have been.</font>

19:13.160 --> 19:15.080
Why not?

19:15.720 --> 19:18.640
I think if you are not my Prime
Minister, you are still my friend?

19:22.320 --> 19:24.200
<font color="#ffff00">I think you must know why.</font>

19:28.760 --> 19:31.840
<font color="#ffff00">A monarch cannot be seen</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to favour one political party.</font>

19:31.880 --> 19:34.760
<font color="#ffff00">You must dine with Robert Peel.</font>

19:34.800 --> 19:39.560
<font color="#ffff00">And he may ask you to make a few</font>
<font color="#ffff00">changes in the Royal household.</font>

19:39.600 --> 19:43.840
<font color="#ffff00">Harriet Sutherland and Emma Portman</font>
<font color="#ffff00">are both married to Whig ministers.</font>

19:43.880 --> 19:46.120
<font color="#ffff00">He will want you to replace them</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with Tory ladies.</font>

19:46.160 --> 19:47.440
But they are my friends!

19:47.480 --> 19:49.440
<font color="#ffff00">I would ask the same in his</font>
<font color="#ffff00">position.</font>

19:49.480 --> 19:52.840
<font color="#ffff00">A Prime Minister must feel he has</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the confidence of his monarch.</font>

19:57.280 --> 20:01.880
Look, these stones are so dirty.
They must be cleaned before we go to
Hanover.

20:01.920 --> 20:04.000
<font color="#00ffff">Hanover will have to wait.</font>

20:04.040 --> 20:08.880
<font color="#00ffff">I think it's going to be far more</font>
<font color="#00ffff">interesting to stay here, now that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Melbourne has gone.</font>

20:08.920 --> 20:12.600
<font color="#00ffff">I do hope the loss won't prove</font>
<font color="#00ffff">too much of a strain on her wits.</font>

20:12.640 --> 20:15.720
Oh, they have never been strong.
Those awful bonnets.

20:15.760 --> 20:19.160
<font color="#00ffff">I heard today, she actually</font>
<font color="#00ffff">went to Dover House quite alone.</font>

20:19.200 --> 20:21.680
<font color="#00ffff">Seems to have lost all sense of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">propriety.</font>

20:21.720 --> 20:23.520
<font color="#00ffff">If this persists...</font>

20:24.440 --> 20:26.400
<font color="#00ffff">..changes will be inevitable.</font>

20:39.480 --> 20:41.040
In a hurry, Sir Robert?

20:41.080 --> 20:42.760
<font color="#ffff00">Her Majesty has sent for me.</font>

20:42.800 --> 20:44.440
Might I offer a word of advice?

20:44.480 --> 20:48.280
Everything will go very smoothly
if you avoid contradicting her.

20:48.320 --> 20:50.640
She does hate to be proved wrong.

20:50.680 --> 20:54.880
<font color="#ffff00">I am sure that she will understand</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the situation when presented with</font>
<font color="#ffff00">facts.</font>

20:54.920 --> 20:59.960
I find that the Queen responds
to a personal approach, a well-told
tale.

21:00.000 --> 21:02.680
She does tend to find the detail
a trifle wearisome.

21:03.680 --> 21:08.120
<font color="#ffff00">I thank you for your advice, but I'm</font>
<font color="#ffff00">sure that we will do very well.</font>

21:08.960 --> 21:12.680
<font color="#ffff00">Her Majesty cannot expect things to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">continue as they did under your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ministry.</font>

21:14.720 --> 21:17.240
<font color="#ffff00">In that case, I wish you a very good</font>
<font color="#ffff00">day.</font>

21:21.640 --> 21:24.280
I have no chin in this one
and two chins in the next.

21:24.320 --> 21:28.840
How can they say it is an accurate
likeness when none of these images
look the same?

21:28.880 --> 21:30.840
<font color="#00ffff">Look at the coin itself, Ma'am.</font>

21:30.880 --> 21:33.080
<font color="#00ffff">It is more convincing in relief, I</font>
<font color="#00ffff">think.</font>

21:33.120 --> 21:35.160
But I look like a goose wearing a
crown.

21:35.200 --> 21:37.480
<font color="#00ff00">Sir Robert Peel.</font>

21:37.960 --> 21:39.400
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty.</font>

21:41.120 --> 21:44.080
Sir Robert, take a look at these
designs for the new coin.

21:44.120 --> 21:45.720
What do you think of this?

21:49.200 --> 21:51.120
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I see nothing wrong with it,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>

21:52.000 --> 21:54.240
<font color="#ffff00">Indeed, I would say it is an</font>
<font color="#ffff00">excellent likeness.</font>

21:54.280 --> 21:56.240
Really?

21:57.240 --> 21:59.520
But you are here on business, Sir
Robert.

21:59.560 --> 22:01.920
<font color="#ffff00">Er...yes, Ma'am.</font>

22:02.840 --> 22:05.680
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps if I might have a private</font>
<font color="#ffff00">audience?</font>

22:18.680 --> 22:23.440
<font color="#ffff00">I am here to assure you that I have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">enough support in the House to form</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a government.</font>

22:23.480 --> 22:25.080
<font color="#ffff00">(Clears throat)</font>

22:25.120 --> 22:27.360
<font color="#ffff00">Of course, as you know, Ma'am,</font>

22:27.400 --> 22:31.040
<font color="#ffff00">any government serves at</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the...pleasure of the Crown.</font>

22:31.720 --> 22:34.000
I do know how the constitution
works.

22:34.040 --> 22:38.800
<font color="#ffff00">And of course, Ma'am, you know it is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">essential that the Crown, that is,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you,</font>

22:38.840 --> 22:43.680
<font color="#ffff00">must appear to be above party</font>
<font color="#ffff00">politics</font>

22:43.720 --> 22:46.280
<font color="#ffff00">and favour neither side over the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">other.</font>

22:46.320 --> 22:49.040
Have you come to give me a lesson
in government, Sir Robert?

22:49.080 --> 22:51.240
<font color="#ffff00">There is the question of your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">household, Ma'am.</font>

22:51.280 --> 22:53.240
My household?

22:53.280 --> 22:58.560
<font color="#ffff00">Four of your ladies are married to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Whig ministers.</font>

22:58.600 --> 23:02.320
<font color="#ffff00">If you were to replace one or two of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">them</font>

23:02.360 --> 23:05.600
<font color="#ffff00">with ladies connected to my side of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the house,</font>

23:05.640 --> 23:10.360
<font color="#ffff00">then there would be no danger of you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">appearing to favour one side.</font>

23:10.400 --> 23:12.360
You want me to give up my ladies?

23:12.400 --> 23:14.720
My closest and dearest friends?

23:14.760 --> 23:16.160
Whatever next, Sir Robert?

23:16.200 --> 23:18.240
My dressers? The housemaids?

23:18.280 --> 23:20.720
Do you want to surround me with
spies?

23:21.960 --> 23:25.440
<font color="#ffff00">It is not my intention to deprive</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you of your friends, Ma'am,</font>

23:25.480 --> 23:27.480
<font color="#ffff00">simply to ask you to be friendly to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">all.</font>

23:27.520 --> 23:29.960
I absolutely will not give up my
ladies, Sir Robert,

23:30.000 --> 23:32.120
and I believe you have no right to
ask me.

23:32.160 --> 23:35.120
<font color="#ffff00">Not even one?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I think I've made myself clear.</font>

23:35.160 --> 23:37.560
Thank you, Sir Robert.

23:50.000 --> 23:54.920
Your mama isn't going to be told
what to do by Sir Robert Peel or
anyone else.

24:02.680 --> 24:05.400
She dismissed me like a footman
caught stealing the silver.

24:05.440 --> 24:09.160
<font color="#ffff00">Hmm! It appears she has her</font>
<font color="#ffff00">grandfather's temper. But she cannot</font>
<font color="#ffff00">refuse you.</font>

24:09.600 --> 24:12.600
I'm afraid she has. She will not
change a single lady.

24:12.640 --> 24:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">Nonsense, man.</font>

24:14.200 --> 24:19.520
<font color="#ffff00">Go back and offer her someone</font>
<font color="#ffff00">charming like, er...Emily Anglesey.</font>

24:19.560 --> 24:24.400
<font color="#ffff00">I am sure her little Majesty would</font>
<font color="#ffff00">exchange her for that cat, Emma</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Portman.</font>

24:24.440 --> 24:28.160
I cannot form a ministry on the
basis of Lady Anglesey's charms.

24:28.200 --> 24:30.520
<font color="#ffff00">No stomach for the fight, eh?</font>

24:30.560 --> 24:34.040
<font color="#ffff00">You should learn to win her over</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like Melbourne does.</font>

24:34.080 --> 24:37.920
I'm afraid I do not have Lord
Melbourne's...ease of manner.

24:37.960 --> 24:41.320
<font color="#ffff00">She would be yours if you would just</font>
<font color="#ffff00">flirt with her a little.</font>

24:41.360 --> 24:46.160
Forgive me. I had not realised that
flirting was a prerequisite for being
Prime Minister.

24:46.200 --> 24:48.560
<font color="#00ffff">Can this really be true? The Tory</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Party,</font>

24:48.600 --> 24:53.520
<font color="#00ffff">the party of Burke and Pitt, has</font>
<font color="#00ffff">been defeated by the caprice of an</font>
<font color="#00ffff">18-year-old girl?</font>

24:53.560 --> 24:56.880
I cannot form a government without
the support of the sovereign.

24:56.920 --> 25:00.640
The Queen refuses to make any
changes to her household. Therefore I
cannot proceed.

25:00.680 --> 25:05.400
<font color="#00ffff">Her behaviour is barely rational.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">To make such a to-do over her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">ladies.</font>

25:05.440 --> 25:10.280
<font color="#00ffff">Mind you, my father behaved in this</font>
<font color="#00ffff">way, at the beginning of his</font>
<font color="#00ffff">affliction.</font>

25:10.320 --> 25:14.160
<font color="#00ffff">If this persists, changes will be</font>
<font color="#00ffff">inevitable!</font>

25:16.280 --> 25:18.920
<font color="#00ff00">Do you know what that...child has</font>
<font color="#00ff00">done?</font>

25:18.960 --> 25:20.480
<font color="#ffff00">No-one tells me anything.</font>

25:20.520 --> 25:26.280
<font color="#00ff00">Your daughter has told Peel she will</font>
<font color="#00ff00">not get rid of any of those Whig</font>
<font color="#00ff00">harpies that surround her</font>

25:26.320 --> 25:29.800
<font color="#00ff00">and now Peel won't form a government</font>
<font color="#00ff00">unless she does.</font>

25:29.840 --> 25:31.960
<font color="#ffff00">No-one can tell Victoria what to do.</font>

25:32.000 --> 25:34.320
<font color="#00ff00">She's trying to get Melbourne back,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of course,</font>

25:34.360 --> 25:39.360
<font color="#00ff00">and if she succeeds, we will not be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">able to protect her with a regency.</font>

25:45.440 --> 25:47.440
<font color="#00ffff">I think I should be the one to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">resign, Ma'am.</font>

25:47.480 --> 25:51.840
<font color="#00ffff">Harriet plays the piano much better</font>
<font color="#00ffff">than me, and she has such an eye for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">fashion.</font>

25:51.880 --> 25:55.160
No-one is going to resign, Emma.
You are my ladies and my friends.

25:55.200 --> 25:58.360
<font color="#ffff00">But, Ma'am, you will have to make</font>
<font color="#ffff00">some adjustments.</font>

25:58.400 --> 26:01.080
<font color="#ffff00">It is the custom when the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">administration changes.</font>

26:01.120 --> 26:04.040
<font color="#00ffff">Otherwise Sir Robert will feel</font>
<font color="#00ffff">he does not have your support,</font>

26:04.080 --> 26:05.960
<font color="#00ffff">and then he cannot form a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">government.</font>

26:08.400 --> 26:11.040
Precisely.

26:24.720 --> 26:27.640
Isn't it rather late for you to be
out, Miss Skerrett?

26:27.680 --> 26:30.920
<font color="#ffff00">I had an errand to run</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and it took longer than expected.</font>

26:30.960 --> 26:34.920
Perhaps that's where I've seen you
before, running errands?

26:35.920 --> 26:38.480
<font color="#ffff00">Not unless you were in Chiswick, Mr</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Francatelli.</font>

26:38.520 --> 26:40.240
No, I've never been to Chiswick,

26:40.280 --> 26:43.400
but I never forget a face,
especially one as pretty as yours.

26:44.720 --> 26:49.320
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sure you've seen many pretty</font>
<font color="#ffff00">faces, Mr Francatelli, but mine</font>
<font color="#ffff00">isn't one of them.</font>

26:54.520 --> 26:57.160
(Bell rings)

26:59.600 --> 27:00.800
<font color="#00ff00">Whoa.</font>

27:04.560 --> 27:05.960
(Snorts snuff)

27:06.000 --> 27:07.560
(Sneezes violently)

27:12.160 --> 27:13.680
There you are, Conroy.

27:13.720 --> 27:18.080
<font color="#00ff00">I confess, I was surprised</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to get your message, sir.</font>

27:18.120 --> 27:22.840
It seems to me, my niece
has taken leave of her wits.

27:22.880 --> 27:24.520
Like my poor father.

27:25.840 --> 27:27.440
<font color="#00ff00">Yes.</font>

27:28.440 --> 27:29.960
<font color="#00ff00">I believe you are right, sir.</font>

27:31.280 --> 27:34.640
<font color="#00ff00">She's always been prone to hysteria,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">ever since she was a child.</font>

27:35.480 --> 27:39.040
<font color="#00ff00">I'm afraid that the strain of her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">position has disordered her senses.</font>

27:39.080 --> 27:41.400
Papa used to talk to himself...

27:42.600 --> 27:45.800
..and scream at nothing in
particular.

27:46.440 --> 27:49.040
Does my niece do anything like that?

27:49.080 --> 27:53.160
<font color="#00ff00">Well, her behaviour is certainly</font>
<font color="#00ff00">erratic, sir, yes. Yes.</font>

27:53.200 --> 27:58.440
No-one wants to believe that the
head that wears the crown is anything
less than sane,

27:58.480 --> 28:02.960
but if needs must, we must not shirk
our duty.

28:04.000 --> 28:05.640
<font color="#00ff00">No, indeed.</font>

28:05.680 --> 28:09.120
I'm sure the Duchess is concerned
for her daughter's welfare.

28:11.240 --> 28:13.160
And I'm worried too...

28:14.760 --> 28:16.480
..for the country.

28:17.080 --> 28:18.680
It may be that...

28:18.720 --> 28:22.880
we can come to some sort of...
arrangement together.

28:23.400 --> 28:25.880
<font color="#00ff00">A regency on the grounds of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">insanity?</font>

28:27.160 --> 28:29.360
You put it bluntly but...

28:29.400 --> 28:32.040
<font color="#00ff00">With the Duchess as Regent?</font>

28:32.080 --> 28:34.840
To be convincing, it would be
necessary

28:34.880 --> 28:38.480
to install a member of the British
royal family

28:38.520 --> 28:40.880
as co-regent.

28:40.920 --> 28:42.400
<font color="#00ff00">(Chuckles)</font>

28:45.200 --> 28:46.920
<font color="#00ff00">Well...</font>

28:48.920 --> 28:52.840
<font color="#00ff00">..I am sure the Duchess will want</font>
<font color="#00ff00">what is best for her daughter.</font>

28:52.880 --> 28:56.680
And for the country.
<font color="#00ff00">That too, sir, of course.</font>

29:06.120 --> 29:08.000
So what will you do now, William?

29:08.040 --> 29:11.720
Now that you don't have to play
nursemaid to your royal charge?

29:12.520 --> 29:18.240
<font color="#ffff00">I shall go to Brocket Hall to finish</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my commentary on the life of St</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Chrysostom.</font>

29:18.280 --> 29:21.000
Little Vicky told Peel she won't
give up a single lady

29:21.040 --> 29:23.240
and she doesn't want him as Prime
Minister.

29:23.280 --> 29:25.440
<font color="#ffff00">It is not her decision to make!</font>

29:27.200 --> 29:29.240
<font color="#00ffff">A message from the Palace, my Lord.</font>

29:29.280 --> 29:32.520
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen would like to see you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at your earliest convenience.</font>

29:34.120 --> 29:37.640
That's your summons.
What are you going to tell her?

29:38.680 --> 29:43.720
<font color="#ffff00">I believe, Emma, that the Queen</font>
<font color="#ffff00">knows the difference between duty</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and inclination.</font>

29:50.560 --> 29:52.680
What have you done to your hand, Mrs
Jenkins?

29:52.720 --> 29:55.640
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, I was trying to light the new</font>
<font color="#00ff00">gas mantle, Ma'am.</font>

29:55.680 --> 29:58.560
Lehzen believes we must
change with the times.

29:58.600 --> 30:01.480
But then she's not the one
who's lighting the gas.

30:01.520 --> 30:04.760
Is it very painful?
<font color="#00ff00">It could have been worse, Ma'am.</font>

30:08.560 --> 30:10.040
(Squeaking)

30:10.880 --> 30:12.360
What was that?

30:12.400 --> 30:14.760
<font color="#00ffff">Probably just the wind, Ma'am.</font>

30:14.800 --> 30:16.320
(Dogs bark)

30:17.800 --> 30:23.000
<font color="#ffff00">Installing the gas downstairs has</font>
<font color="#ffff00">disturbed the rats. They're looking</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for new territory.</font>

30:23.040 --> 30:25.120
<font color="#00ffff">I saw one in the throne room this</font>
<font color="#00ffff">morning!</font>

30:25.160 --> 30:28.200
The throne room?
<font color="#ffff00">Indeed, Baroness.</font>

30:28.240 --> 30:32.120
<font color="#ffff00">They're spreading through the palace</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like a miasma of corruption.</font>

30:32.160 --> 30:34.000
But you will deal with them, Mr
Penge.

30:34.040 --> 30:37.280
<font color="#ffff00">Certainly, but it will be an</font>
<font color="#ffff00">expensive business.</font>

30:56.520 --> 30:58.440
Dear Lord M.

30:58.760 --> 31:01.200
Don't you think I've arranged things
marvellously?

31:01.240 --> 31:04.680
<font color="#ffff00">You have been most resourceful,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Sir Robert was so rough with me.</font>

31:04.720 --> 31:09.240
He wanted to send all my ladies away
and replace them with some horrid
Tory spies.

31:09.280 --> 31:13.320
<font color="#ffff00">Peel is a...he's a fine politician</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and a man of principle</font>

31:13.360 --> 31:17.880
<font color="#ffff00">but I fear he has never understood</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the fairer sex.</font>

31:20.360 --> 31:21.520
I have missed you.

31:21.560 --> 31:23.880
<font color="#ffff00">(Chuckles) It's been all of a day</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and a half.</font>

31:24.760 --> 31:29.040
<font color="#ffff00">And whilst I salute your tenacity,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am, I must tell you</font>

31:29.080 --> 31:31.600
<font color="#ffff00">that if I were to return</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as Prime Minister,</font>

31:31.640 --> 31:33.200
<font color="#ffff00">it would not be in your interests.</font>

31:33.240 --> 31:34.960
Not in my interests?

31:35.680 --> 31:37.600
But it is all that I desire in the
world.

31:37.640 --> 31:39.280
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you flatter me, Ma'am,</font>

31:39.320 --> 31:43.240
<font color="#ffff00">but I cannot allow you to jeopardise</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the position of the Crown on my</font>
<font color="#ffff00">account.</font>

31:43.280 --> 31:45.520
Allow me?
<font color="#ffff00">Peel was perfectly within his rights</font>

31:45.560 --> 31:47.800
<font color="#ffff00">to ask you to make some changes</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in your household.</font>

31:47.840 --> 31:52.440
If I lose them, I will have no-one!
It'll be like Kensington all over
again.

31:53.320 --> 31:55.960
Peel does not understand this, but
you do.

31:56.000 --> 31:59.320
<font color="#ffff00">But he does deserve your support.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">A monarch must be seen to be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">impartial.</font>

31:59.360 --> 32:02.640
I can't help it if all my friends
are Whigs!
<font color="#ffff00">Because that's all you know.</font>

32:02.680 --> 32:05.880
I don't believe if Sir Robert had
been my Prime Minister from the
first,

32:05.920 --> 32:08.840
I would ever have liked him
half as much as I like you.

32:08.880 --> 32:11.960
<font color="#ffff00">You are still young and</font>
<font color="#ffff00">inexperienced,</font>

32:12.000 --> 32:17.080
<font color="#ffff00">and it is my job, no, it is my duty,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to see that you come to no harm.</font>

32:17.120 --> 32:18.840
<font color="#ffff00">If I were to form a government now,</font>

32:18.880 --> 32:22.600
<font color="#ffff00">critics would say that I had</font>
<font color="#ffff00">manipulated you for my own</font>
<font color="#ffff00">advantage.</font>

32:22.640 --> 32:25.080
I am not a piece of clay
to be moulded by any hand.

32:25.120 --> 32:29.760
<font color="#ffff00">No, indeed, but you must understand</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that it doesn't matter who you like</font>
<font color="#ffff00">or do not like!</font>

32:29.800 --> 32:32.600
How can you say that? Surely my
inclinations are paramount.

32:32.640 --> 32:35.400
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty, surely you understand</font>
<font color="#ffff00">what is at stake here?</font>

32:35.440 --> 32:37.760
Lord Melbourne, you forget yourself!

32:38.800 --> 32:41.160
Don't you want to be my Prime
Minister?

32:43.800 --> 32:45.680
<font color="#ffff00">Not in these circumstances.</font>

32:47.040 --> 32:50.960
<font color="#ffff00">The relationship between Crown</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and Parliament is a sacred one</font>

32:51.000 --> 32:53.520
<font color="#ffff00">and I will not allow you to put it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in danger.</font>

33:03.760 --> 33:08.800
<font color="#00ffff">Drina can be foolish, and headstrong</font>
<font color="#00ffff">maybe, but she's not mad.</font>

33:08.840 --> 33:13.000
<font color="#00ff00">Visiting Melbourne at his house on a</font>
<font color="#00ff00">whim is hardly rational.</font>

33:14.160 --> 33:15.720
<font color="#00ff00">I suppose he had a mad wife,</font>

33:15.760 --> 33:20.320
<font color="#00ff00">so this kind of behaviour is quite</font>
<font color="#00ff00">unexceptional to him, but it is not</font>
<font color="#00ff00">fitting in the Queen.</font>

33:21.320 --> 33:24.080
<font color="#00ffff">She is a young girl with a tendresse</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for a man.</font>

33:24.120 --> 33:26.360
<font color="#00ffff">It is not so unusual.</font>

33:26.400 --> 33:29.320
<font color="#00ff00">A spell of calm and seclusion is</font>
<font color="#00ff00">what she needs,</font>

33:29.360 --> 33:31.920
<font color="#00ff00">sequestered from the cares of her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">position.</font>

33:31.960 --> 33:34.760
<font color="#00ffff">No, that is too much.</font>

33:35.400 --> 33:36.760
<font color="#00ffff">I want to help her.</font>

33:36.800 --> 33:39.800
<font color="#00ff00">This is the best way to help her.</font>

33:41.640 --> 33:43.600
<font color="#00ff00">My dear Duchess...</font>

33:44.280 --> 33:47.160
<font color="#00ff00">you know how much I want you to take</font>
<font color="#00ff00">your rightful place</font>

33:47.200 --> 33:49.040
<font color="#00ff00">as Regent.</font>

34:01.520 --> 34:03.280
Sir.

34:06.240 --> 34:08.400
<font color="#ffff00">Brandy. In the library.</font>

34:09.639 --> 34:11.320
<font color="#ffff00">And I'm not at home...</font>

34:12.000 --> 34:13.800
<font color="#ffff00">to anyone.</font>

34:46.400 --> 34:48.480
(Exhales)

34:49.400 --> 34:51.239
I couldn't sleep.

34:52.960 --> 34:55.360
<font color="#00ffff">You need to be rested for your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">birthday celebration.</font>

34:55.400 --> 34:57.240
<font color="#00ffff">Let me take you back to your room.</font>

34:57.280 --> 34:58.800
(Squeaking)

34:58.840 --> 35:01.440
Mama, did you hear that?

35:01.480 --> 35:03.120
<font color="#00ffff">My poor little girl.</font>

35:03.160 --> 35:08.040
<font color="#00ffff">You must not start at shadows,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">or people will whisper about you.</font>

35:08.080 --> 35:10.320
<font color="#00ffff">They remember your grandfather.</font>

35:11.320 --> 35:12.920
My grandfather?

35:15.480 --> 35:16.920
But he was mad.

35:16.960 --> 35:18.400
What are you saying, Mama?

35:18.760 --> 35:20.600
<font color="#00ffff">It is not what I am saying.</font>

35:20.640 --> 35:23.400
<font color="#00ffff">But maybe you're needing some rest</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and quiet.</font>

35:27.200 --> 35:29.120
<font color="#00ffff">I will protect you, Drina.</font>

35:30.360 --> 35:33.400
<font color="#00ffff">I will not let them take it away</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from you.</font>

35:35.560 --> 35:40.040
There was a time, Mama,
when I needed your protection.

35:43.400 --> 35:46.280
But instead you allowed Sir John
to make you his creature.

35:47.280 --> 35:50.040
<font color="#00ffff">Sir John at least cares about my</font>
<font color="#00ffff">existence.</font>

35:50.080 --> 35:52.680
<font color="#00ffff">You have banished me from your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">affections.</font>

35:52.720 --> 35:54.840
And whose fault is that, Mama?

36:04.360 --> 36:06.640
<font color="#ffff00">Do you want any particular style,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am?</font>

36:12.840 --> 36:15.160
I can't seem to fix on anything
today.

36:22.320 --> 36:24.120
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Penge, a word.</font>

36:24.840 --> 36:28.320
<font color="#00ffff">Her Majesty heard a rustling last</font>
<font color="#00ffff">night in the sitting room.</font>

36:28.360 --> 36:33.040
<font color="#00ffff">I told her it was nothing. I hope I</font>
<font color="#00ffff">was correct.</font>

36:33.080 --> 36:35.120
<font color="#ffff00">I hope so too, Baroness,</font>

36:35.160 --> 36:40.320
<font color="#ffff00">but when you upset the natural order</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of things with your gas lighting,</font>

36:40.360 --> 36:42.280
<font color="#ffff00">the consequences are far-reaching.</font>

36:43.840 --> 36:48.320
<font color="#00ff00"># God save our gracious Queen</font>

36:48.360 --> 36:52.200
<font color="#00ff00"># Long live our noble Queen</font>

36:52.240 --> 36:56.640
<font color="#00ff00"># God save the Queen...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Look. Oh, it's dear little Dash.</font>

36:58.280 --> 37:01.560
Who made this?
<font color="#ffff00">Mr Francatelli, Your Majesty.</font>

37:01.600 --> 37:03.440
<font color="#ffff00">The Palace Chef.</font>

37:03.480 --> 37:05.320
I must congratulate you, Penge.

37:05.360 --> 37:07.880
It has all been done very prettily.

37:08.920 --> 37:12.360
<font color="#00ff00"># God save our Queen</font>

37:16.280 --> 37:18.320
Mama.

37:18.360 --> 37:20.040
<font color="#00ffff">Happy Birthday, Victoria.</font>

37:20.760 --> 37:23.480
<font color="#00ff00">May I add my best wishes</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on your birthday, Ma'am.</font>

37:23.520 --> 37:27.120
<font color="#00ff00">Your first of many more as Queen, I</font>
<font color="#00ff00">hope.</font>

37:30.040 --> 37:32.520
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps you'd like to open your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">presents, Ma'am?</font>

37:37.040 --> 37:39.280
<font color="#ffff00">From Lord Melbourne, Ma'am.</font>

38:04.760 --> 38:07.320
He thinks I would benefit
from studying the heavens.

38:08.800 --> 38:10.640
<font color="#00ffff">Happy Birthday.</font>

38:12.480 --> 38:14.640
Thank you, Mama.

38:16.880 --> 38:18.600
A volume of Shakespeare.

38:19.680 --> 38:21.960
"King Lear."

38:22.000 --> 38:26.280
"How sharper than a serpent's tooth
it is to have a thankless child."

38:28.480 --> 38:31.040
(Squeaking)
(Screaming)

38:36.800 --> 38:38.920
<font color="#00ff00">Calm yourself!</font>

38:38.960 --> 38:41.480
<font color="#00ff00">Ma'am! Ma'am! Calm yourself!</font>

38:41.520 --> 38:43.920
Hysterics. (Inhales)

38:44.560 --> 38:46.240
Over a rat?

38:46.280 --> 38:48.200
<font color="#00ff00">You could hear her all over the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Palace.</font>

38:48.240 --> 38:51.720
Was there a rat, or was it an
hallucination?

38:52.560 --> 38:55.160
My father used to see a red dog.

38:55.920 --> 38:57.680
<font color="#00ff00">I believe there was a rat...</font>

38:58.560 --> 39:01.440
<font color="#00ff00">..but the Queen's reaction was,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">er...excessive.</font>

39:01.480 --> 39:05.400
It must raise the question
as to the state of her wits.

39:05.440 --> 39:08.760
I wonder if Wellington and Peel
will feel the same way.

39:08.800 --> 39:14.560
Peel may put aside his scruples
when he realises what is at stake.

39:16.560 --> 39:21.200
<font color="#00ff00">The Duchess...wants no harm</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to come to her daughter.</font>

39:22.840 --> 39:25.040
We will care for her together.

39:26.200 --> 39:27.920
Together.

39:29.800 --> 39:34.800
<font color="#ffff00">I believe, Ma'am, that your nerves</font>
<font color="#ffff00">have been under considerable strain.</font>

39:34.840 --> 39:39.600
<font color="#ffff00">You must have complete rest,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">so that your equilibrium can be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">restored.</font>

39:39.640 --> 39:43.120
Out of the question.
I have an engagement this afternoon.

39:43.160 --> 39:44.920
<font color="#ffff00">But, Ma'am, you are not yourself.</font>

39:44.960 --> 39:48.360
I had a shock, Sir James, that is
all.

39:49.320 --> 39:51.280
I am not an invalid.

39:51.320 --> 39:53.720
<font color="#00ff00">(Whispers) The strain is too much</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for her.</font>

39:53.760 --> 39:59.080
<font color="#00ffff">There was one the size of a baby,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and not a new-born one neither.</font>

39:59.120 --> 40:00.600
<font color="#00ffff">(Laughter)</font>

40:01.080 --> 40:04.240
<font color="#ffff00">Baroness, how may I help you?</font>

40:04.280 --> 40:09.040
<font color="#00ff00">I came to tell you that I have</font>
<font color="#00ff00">decided not to install gas at the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Palace.</font>

40:10.360 --> 40:12.440
<font color="#00ff00">It has caused too much disturbance.</font>

40:12.480 --> 40:15.160
<font color="#ffff00">As you wish, Baroness.</font>

40:18.600 --> 40:20.480
<font color="#ffff00">(They snigger)</font>

40:20.520 --> 40:25.280
<font color="#00ffff">I'd heard reports of...an incident</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on your birthday and I was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">concerned.</font>

40:25.320 --> 40:28.200
I am in perfect health, as you see.

40:28.240 --> 40:33.680
<font color="#00ffff">Then you must be aware that it is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">time for you to call someone to form</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a government, Ma'am.</font>

40:33.720 --> 40:38.440
<font color="#00ffff">I know Peel is not a charmer like</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Melbourne, but, er...he's sound</font>
<font color="#00ffff">enough.</font>

40:38.480 --> 40:41.720
Very possibly. But I will not give
up my ladies.

40:42.200 --> 40:44.160
They are my allies.

40:44.200 --> 40:45.800
You were a soldier, Duke.

40:45.840 --> 40:47.640
Would you want to go into battle
alone?

40:47.680 --> 40:51.280
<font color="#00ffff">I was not aware that you were</font>
<font color="#00ffff">fighting a war, Ma'am.</font>

40:51.320 --> 40:53.680
Because you are not a young woman,
Duke,

40:53.720 --> 40:56.440
and no-one, I suspect, tells you
what to do.

40:57.320 --> 40:59.840
But I have to prove my worth every
single day.

41:00.800 --> 41:02.320
And I cannot do it alone.

41:07.640 --> 41:11.720
<font color="#ffff00">MAN IN CROWD:</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Robert Peel for Prime Minister!</font>

41:11.760 --> 41:14.040
I wonder if I should wave at the
crowd?

41:15.520 --> 41:17.840
No-one seems to be smiling.

41:18.400 --> 41:21.080
<font color="#00ffff">MAN: Who's running the country?</font>

41:23.040 --> 41:25.520
<font color="#00ff00">(Woman in crowd shouts out)</font>

41:27.280 --> 41:29.720
<font color="#00ffff">This situation is getting out of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">hand, Melbourne.</font>

41:29.760 --> 41:33.160
<font color="#00ffff">Cumberland thinks the little Queen</font>
<font color="#00ffff">listens to voices in her head,</font>

41:33.200 --> 41:34.920
<font color="#00ffff">like her grandfather.</font>

41:36.200 --> 41:39.400
<font color="#00ffff">If he's right, we'll have to appoint</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a regent.</font>

41:39.440 --> 41:42.560
<font color="#00ffff">Must have someone sensible</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at the heart of things.</font>

41:42.600 --> 41:44.240
<font color="#ffff00">You cannot mean that, sir.</font>

41:44.280 --> 41:47.400
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps not, but I am not the man</font>

41:47.440 --> 41:51.880
<font color="#00ffff">to put those rumours to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">rest...Melbourne.</font>

41:59.760 --> 42:02.600
<font color="#00ff00">LORD CHANCELLOR:</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Her Majesty, Queen Victoria.</font>

42:19.720 --> 42:21.880
<font color="#00ffff">Welcome, Your Majesty.</font>

42:45.680 --> 42:48.680
<font color="#ffff00">May I be of assistance, Ma'am?</font>

42:48.720 --> 42:51.440
I should be most grateful.

42:51.480 --> 42:53.520
It seems I can't manage unaided.

42:55.400 --> 42:58.400
<font color="#ffff00">Then it will be my pleasure to serve</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you, Ma'am.</font>

43:01.800 --> 43:03.800
Do you mean...?

43:04.400 --> 43:08.080
<font color="#ffff00">If you do me the honour of asking me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to form a ministry, Ma'am,</font>

43:08.120 --> 43:09.840
<font color="#ffff00">then I would accept.</font>

43:18.400 --> 43:20.280
(Appreciative murmurs from crowd)

43:24.760 --> 43:28.800
<font color="#ffff00">No picture could truly do you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">justice, Ma'am, but this comes</font>
<font color="#ffff00">close.</font>

43:31.760 --> 43:33.880
(Chuckles)

43:33.920 --> 43:35.640
<font color="#00ff00">And that is the Lord's Anointed.</font>

43:35.920 --> 43:38.080
<font color="#00ffff">The public like having a young</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Queen.</font>

43:38.120 --> 43:41.320
<font color="#00ffff">It makes the country feel youthful,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">don't you know.</font>

43:41.560 --> 43:44.880
<font color="#00ff00">No-one wants a Queen who has lost</font>
<font color="#00ff00">her reason.</font>

43:44.920 --> 43:48.480
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, I think the Queen looks</font>
<font color="#00ffff">eminently sane.</font>

43:48.520 --> 43:51.240
<font color="#00ffff">See, she has Melbourne by her side</font>
<font color="#00ffff">again.</font>

43:51.280 --> 43:55.400
<font color="#00ffff">I expect that he caught wind of your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">plans</font>

43:55.440 --> 43:57.200
<font color="#00ffff">and decided he would not have it.</font>

43:57.240 --> 43:59.320
<font color="#00ff00">My plans?</font>

43:59.360 --> 44:02.880
<font color="#00ff00">I have no desire</font>
<font color="#00ff00">other than for a Tory government.</font>

44:03.560 --> 44:09.160
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, we shall be in office soon</font>
<font color="#00ffff">enough, but in the right</font>
<font color="#00ffff">circumstances.</font>

44:23.640 --> 44:26.240
Oh, you are a very fine piece.

44:26.280 --> 44:28.160
<font color="#ffff00">Let me go. I am not for sale.</font>

44:28.200 --> 44:30.960
Everyone is for sale.
It just depends on the price.

44:31.000 --> 44:33.400
<font color="#ffff00">Really, sir, I'm not...</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Please, leave the lady alone.</font>

44:33.440 --> 44:35.240
And who are you, her protector?
<font color="#00ffff">No.</font>

44:35.280 --> 44:37.000
<font color="#00ffff">Her friend.</font>

44:43.520 --> 44:45.520
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

44:45.560 --> 44:48.360
<font color="#00ffff">You are more complicated than I</font>
<font color="#00ffff">thought, Miss Skerrett.</font>

44:48.960 --> 44:50.280
<font color="#00ffff">I knew I'd seen you before.</font>

44:50.320 --> 44:53.800
<font color="#00ffff">Ma Fletcher's nunnery, if I'm not</font>
<font color="#00ffff">mistaken?</font>

44:53.840 --> 44:58.000
<font color="#00ffff">Now the question is, how you got</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from a house of ill repute to the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Queen's dressing room?</font>

44:58.040 --> 44:59.400
<font color="#ffff00">That's my business.</font>

44:59.440 --> 45:02.840
<font color="#ffff00">Please...don't tell on me, Mr</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Francatelli.</font>

45:02.880 --> 45:06.120
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, don't worry, Miss Skerrett.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I don't care where you come from.</font>

45:07.120 --> 45:10.600
<font color="#00ffff">I'm just looking forward</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to getting better acquainted.</font>

45:17.880 --> 45:22.720
<font color="#ffff00">So young and with such</font>
<font color="#ffff00">responsibilities.</font>

45:22.760 --> 45:24.960
<font color="#ffff00">She should not have to bear them</font>
<font color="#ffff00">alone.</font>

45:25.000 --> 45:27.840
<font color="#00ffff">I am so glad William has agreed</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to form a ministry.</font>

45:27.880 --> 45:30.440
<font color="#00ffff">You have arranged things very well,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ma'am.</font>

45:30.480 --> 45:35.160
I outflanked my enemies,
as the Duke of Wellington would say.

45:35.200 --> 45:36.960
<font color="#00ffff">(They chuckle)</font>

45:37.000 --> 45:39.960
<font color="#00ff00">But you do know that your days are</font>
<font color="#00ff00">numbered, don't you?</font>

45:40.000 --> 45:42.640
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, of course.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Any Prime Minister knows that.</font>

45:42.680 --> 45:46.120
<font color="#00ff00">I mean, that the Queen must marry</font>
<font color="#00ff00">soon.</font>

45:46.160 --> 45:48.280
<font color="#00ff00">And then...</font>

45:48.320 --> 45:50.120
<font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

45:50.760 --> 45:53.880
<font color="#ffff00">Then she will look to her husband,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">not to me.</font>

45:55.400 --> 45:57.160
<font color="#ffff00">I know.</font>

46:01.680 --> 46:05.280
<font color="#ffff00">There has been an uprising by a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">group calling themselves Chartists.</font>

46:06.000 --> 46:07.960
<font color="#00ffff">You must talk to Victoria about</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Albert.</font>

46:08.120 --> 46:10.720
<font color="#00ff00">I have seen the way my niece looks</font>
<font color="#00ff00">at you.</font>

46:11.040 --> 46:13.640
I don't want to stupid boy like
Albert or anyone else!

46:13.720 --> 46:16.960
<font color="#ffff00">I believe when you give your heart,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it will be without hesitation.</font>

46:18.240 --> 46:21.160
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know what it is you want but</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you ain't getting nothing from me.</font>

46:21.200 --> 46:23.120
We cannot marry where we please you
and I.

46:23.160 --> 46:26.400
<font color="#00ff00">Victoria does not care for the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">admirable Conroy</font>

46:26.600 --> 46:28.000
<font color="#00ffff">I cannot live without him.</font>

46:28.040 --> 46:29.920
I think I will never be happy.

